parameters.name: SC_X
parameters.description: Spacecraft jovicentric (Jupiter fixed) X position, along the Jupiter-Sun line in the solar equatorial plane (positive towards the Sun), in the unit of Jovian radii.

parameters.name: SC_Y
parameters.description: Spacecraft jovicentric (Jupiter fixed) Y position, completing the right handed, orthogonal set, in the unit of Jovian radii.

parameters.name: SC_Z
parameters.description: Spacecraft jovicentric (Jupiter fixed) Z position, along the Jovian spin axis, in the unit of Jovian radii.

parameters.name: VEL_X
parameters.description: Spacecraft velocity jovicentric X component, along the Jupiter-Sun line in the solar equatorial plane (positive towards the Sun), in the unit of kilometers/second.

parameters.name: VEL_Y
parameters.description: Spacecraft velocity jovicentric Y component, completing the right handed, orthogonal set, in the unit of kilometers/second.

parameters.name: VEL_Z
parameters.description: Spacecraft velocity jovicentric Z component, along the Jovian spin axis, in the unit of kilometers/second.

parameters.name: SC_R
parameters.description: Jupiter to spacecraft range (positive away from Jupiter) in the unit of Jovian radii.

parameters.name: SC_LON
parameters.description: Jovicentric east longitude, completing the left handed, orthogonal set in degrees.

parameters.name: CARTSYS3_TO_SPHSYS3
parameters.description: This column contains the 9 1pe15.8 rotation matrix elements for converting from Cartesian System III to Spherical System III coordinates.

parameters.name: SC_TO_CARTSYS3
parameters.description: This column contains the 9 1pe15.8 rotation matrix elements for converting from Payload (Spacecraft) to Cartesian System III coordinates.

parameters.name: SC_TO_SPHSYS3
parameters.description: This column contains the 9 1pe15.8 rotation matrix elements for converting from Payload (Spacecraft) to Spherical System III coordinates.
